    dc:description "Figure 3. Trapezionida brachytes (Macpherson, 1994), female, 3.7 mm (MNHN-IU- 2017 - 2926), New Caledonia A carapace and pleon, dorsal view B sternal plastron C cephalic region, showing antennular and antennal peduncles, ventral view D right Mxp 3 ischium and merus, lateral view E right P 1, dorsal view F right P 2, lateral view G dactylus of right P 2, lateral view H right P 3, lateral view I right P 4, lateral view. Scale bars: 1.0 mm (A, E, F, H, I); 0.5 mm (B, C, D, G)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/961266" ;
